snippet.title: Gori: Cuddly Carnage - Official Gameplay Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
Gori introduces an adorable murder-kitty who has to fight through hordes of mutant unicorns in this futuristic world. Labeled as a 'Skate n slash' where Gori zips around on his razor-sharp hoverboard to save the world, Gori is a fast-paced action game that is sure to get your interest purring. Here is the gameplay trailer for Gori: Cuddly Carnage.

#IGN #Gaming #IGNSummerOfGaming
